          Shell Limestone
          
        </term>
            </rs> or <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">for Coal</hi>
            <lb/>
A gain (when <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag4"
                ref="#chemical_184"
                type="chemical">
               <term xml:id="tag4">
          Shell Limestone
          
        </term>
            </rs> is found there<lb/>
is a strong <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
