               <term xml:id="tag7">
                  <hi rend="underline">Pit coal</hi>
               </term>
            </rs> would exist.-<lb/>
These circumstances which are <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">fundamental</del>
            <lb/>
fundamental facts of the science prove in<lb/>
a strong manner that considerable<lb/>
discoveries may often result from Geological<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="9"
                xml:id="pb-9"
                facs="#i9"/>
            <lb/>
Knowledge and that it affords information<lb/>
capable of being immediately brought into use -<lb/>
The person who is diggin for <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag8"
