               <term xml:id="tag11">
          Granite
          
        </term>
            </rs>, it affords<lb/>
him immediate encouragement to proceed<lb/>
in his researches -<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                n="10"
                xml:id="pb-10"
                facs="#i10"/>
            <lb/>
And a yellow of red <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
