For these Rocks are generally immediately<lb/>
incumbent on Coal.-<lb/>
Similar reasoning may be applied to <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">metallic</hi>
            <lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
