                rend="underline">springs arise</hi> that<lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">it is</hi> his business to divert -<lb/>
And the improver of land may often<lb/>
derive from Geology very useful instructions<lb/>
with regard to <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
